The,cross,io,platform,allows,developers,to,create,Web,and,Mobile,Syndication,between,a,large,number,of,API,Services,When,integrating,the,cross,io,platform,developers,gain,access,to,over,web,services,with,which,they,can,syndicate,between,The,RESTful,API,also,provides,functionality,such,as,schedule,filter,delay,sample,translate,trigger,and,optimize,which,let,developers,extend,the,connection,between,services,The,API,is,currently,in,closed,beta